NAME Random Password Gen
DESCRIPTION Types a batch of random passwords into any text field
CATEGORY post
PLATFORMS WIN,MAC,LINUX
OPTION COUNT 5 "Number of passwords to generate"
OPTION LENGTH 16 "Password length"
OPTION DELAY 500 "Initial delay (ms)"
PLATFORM ALL
DELAY {{DELAY}}
LED_COLOR CYAN
REPEAT_BLOCK {{COUNT}}
STRING Password: 
RANDOM_STRING {{LENGTH}}
ENTER
DELAY 100
END_REPEAT
LED_COLOR GREEN
